cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this dataset or pipeline, please cite the manuscript and the dataset as below."
title: "soap-sbar-llm-benchmark: Fact-Transcription Fidelity in LLM SOAP-to-SBAR Translation (Dataset and Pipeline)"
abstract: >
  Reproducibility package for the three-stage automated evaluation pipeline
  applied to fact-transcription fidelity benchmarking of GPT-4o, Claude Opus 4.5,
  and Gemini 2.5 Flash-Lite on SOAP-to-SBAR translation. Includes 9 source SOAP
  scenarios, 180 pre-specified fact tags, 1,620 generated SBAR records, all
  analysis scripts, and per-call resolved_model logs.
